Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:39.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:44.55,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎しみに　変わって行く前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:46.52,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何もかもそうだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:51.54,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:56.70,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:02:00.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:04.94,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:12.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壊しあって　解り合ったことも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:14.37,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:17.81,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:22.35,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:28.56,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:33.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:40.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:45.39,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って君はつぶやいて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:50.05,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信じる事が怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.30,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:56.06,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:03:01.08,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本当の愛を知るだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.20,0:01:39.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱说爱「过于沉重」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.92,0:01:44.55,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在转变成恨之前　把它拒绝于心门之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.69,0:01:46.52,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万物皆是如此吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.64,0:01:51.54,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是把不合时宜的事隐藏起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是冒牌货的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.48,0:01:56.70,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在扭曲了的窘迫时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:02:00.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连本应定下约定的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:04.94,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会毫无察觉地擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.61,0:02:12.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那开始崩坏但曾经互相理解的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.74,0:02:14.37,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其撇下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.49,0:02:17.81,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的末路吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:22.35,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心中不服　想与之对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.96,0:02:28.56,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要从当初堕落的印象中逃离开去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:33.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊　就算历经千百次也要找出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:40.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的双眸　你手中的余温
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:45.39,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小声嘟囔着「爱总是让我遍体鳞伤…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:50.05,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因畏惧坚信不疑的事而哭过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.24,0:02:52.30,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道软弱才能变强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.45,0:02:56.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要害怕坚信不疑地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.18,0:03:01.08,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是爱的真谛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}三个月前  拉格朗日3
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.12,0:00:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive  连接完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.15,0:00:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive  连接完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认已经连接
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.34,0:00:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO各部分一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.11,0:00:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两架太阳炉均正常运转中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.09,0:00:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  开始协调测试
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.78,0:00:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧  特瑞亚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.30,0:00:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive  REPAUSE解除
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:37.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓扑缺陷由既定状态向高位推移
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.42,0:00:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twin-Drive的粒子同步率
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,35  37  40  47
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.24,0:00:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,49  55  58
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:50.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破了60%
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.66,0:00:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超过80%  就能进入稳定活动领域
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.35,0:00:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓扑缺陷发生不稳定因素
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:01.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twin-Drive搭载率低下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.15,0:01:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融合率也处于下降中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来  所有的搭配都尝试过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:18.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么会不稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.02,0:01:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底缺什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.84,0:01:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下Exia的太阳炉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.86,0:01:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想在那些家伙行动之前做些什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的希望  Exia的GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:11.00,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}#02  Twin-Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干什么  把人叫出来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.25,0:03:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然说自己是Celestial Being…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼尔·迪兰地曾经是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥是…Gundam Meister？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  他生前驾驶过Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生前驾驶过…？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道  哥哥已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死于四年前的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想让我继承哥哥的遗志吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:47.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:50.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你也和尼尔·迪兰地一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.57,0:03:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想改变这个世界的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且有为此战斗的觉悟的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.89,0:04:03.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里存有我们的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  如果我把这个交给保安局的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.30,0:04:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安局马上要对欧洲卡塔隆地下指挥部进行镇压
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:19.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是来真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.99,0:04:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是卡蒂·马内金上校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚前来赴任
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你的到来  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所知
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们独立治安维持部队A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:37.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了铲除反联邦势力而设立的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直隶于联邦政府的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打击对象是持有军事力量的非联邦参加国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.42,0:04:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自称卡塔隆的反政府组织
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有…另一个是上校你应该很熟悉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.05,0:04:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他们再次采取武力介入的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方部队就必须与之对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:04.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舆论也会站在我方一边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.84,0:05:12.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我十分看好与Gundam有着实战经验的你的才干
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:14.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在A-LAWS尽情地施展拳脚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立治安维持部队A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦忠实的看家狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以坐下吗  上校
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩丽丝中尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也在A-LAWS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:31.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:34.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接到征集命令  昨天到任的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.80,0:05:37.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯密尔诺夫上校居然能同意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面的命令是不能违背的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.55,0:05:41.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.81,0:05:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈·斯密尔诺夫  军衔是少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:48.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯密尔诺夫？难道是斯密尔诺夫上校的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是他儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把AEU的作战指挥官以及人革联的超兵都集中起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是片桐司令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.78,0:05:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应对神速
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  返回指挥所的同时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始Exia太阳炉的协调测试
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协调模拟中Exia和O Gundam太阳炉的联动率应该很高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:17.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(O GUNDAM: GN-000 GN系列GUNDAM的始祖机，\N即刹那曾经看到的那台)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:20.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不实测一下是不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚·修亨伯格\N把新Gundam主发动机理论与TRANS-AM一起留给了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只靠纸上谈兵就能对200年后的科学水平进行了预测吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭载两个太阳炉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:36.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子产量指数化
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.16,0:06:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是OO的Twin-Drive系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:50.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送饭来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在这了  一定要吃哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  我把红哈罗也放在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照  请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:01.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事找我们请跟红哈罗说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数据库也可以随意阅览
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们想把我关到什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.16,0:07:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被A-LAWS盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是什么卡塔隆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是对方也这么想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们还想进行武力介入吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是与A-LAWS战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与联邦军？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府直派的独立部队
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们已以镇压为名进行了14次屠杀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇难者达到数万人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一消息已被封锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也领教过他们的做法了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联邦政府不就是在你们的武力干预下建立起来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:54.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  才要做个了结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续战斗  又会把无辜的人牵扯进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:08:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不战斗的话  人还是会死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾恩先生  测试差不多要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.61,0:08:06.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他呢？刹那在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.35,0:08:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去接人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接我们的同伴去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你实在喝得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样我可照顾不过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.00,0:08:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见  比利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你两年的照顾  后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:46.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  九条
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是这个意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来客人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.11,0:08:56.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会把这里告诉别人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  还可以请他一起吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔叙叙旧也好嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹…刹那…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年没见了  皇·李·诺瑞加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊  她的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行动代号  皇·李·诺瑞加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.43,0:09:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的战术预报员
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.99,0:09:37.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来你无处可逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.86,0:09:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保安局的镇压是真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  受害者呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:48.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.05,0:09:50.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后再联络
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是GIN1  请求立刻联络
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于事态紧急  请求直接面谈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia和O Gundam的协调虽然达到了目前最高数值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍超不过70%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.65,0:10:14.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离稳定范围还有10%
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用TRANS-AM强制启动的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:18.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.91,0:10:21.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一来导致超负荷的话  最糟糕的情况就是自爆了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再对系统进行一次检测
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.82,0:10:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西班牙对平民的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:35.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被判断是Gundam Throne所为
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.71,0:10:39.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击理由：不明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Throne？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne的机体并不在本计划之中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne还搭载了疑似GN Drive的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.31,0:10:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放射出的攻击型粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.34,0:10:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会对人体产生影响
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:56.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影响人体？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:10:58.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.58,0:11:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能对左手进行再生治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说Gundam的光束兵器中带有对再生细胞有害的元素
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Throne
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这架机体把路易丝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是敌人  他们是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:15.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们是敌人  他们是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我带来想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:26.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算成立了联邦政府  世界也丝毫没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明牺牲了这么多人  却没有任何改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚的计划毫无意义
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.10,0:11:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是借酒消愁的理由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经厌倦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.86,0:11:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事情我做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我们还会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.72,0:11:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果促使世界变革是我们的罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要赎罪就只能使世界再次改变
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:58.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃避吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.35,0:12:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避有什么不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.50,0:12:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有你那么坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.15,0:12:06.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向同步卫星轨道空间站出发
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.94,0:12:10.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开往Grand Union的特急班机F1200…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:12.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说刹那  不要管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.78,0:12:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有新的Meister会来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.50,0:12:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的…Meister？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.82,0:12:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟  好迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.82,0:12:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩…怎么  还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有这么像吗  我和哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.04,0:12:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.23,0:12:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍  他是莱尔·迪兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.85,0:12:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  我叫洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:42.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克劳斯  GIN1已经与Celestial Being接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:46.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}卡塔隆中东支部  地下设施
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟会不会协助我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以太阳光系统输电权为把柄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迫使参加国对其唯命是从
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.97,0:12:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对非参加国则采取弃而不管的政策
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.86,0:12:54.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在联邦这做法实在是惨无人道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且联邦过于急迫实行统一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:59.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进而成立了直属的治安维持部队
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企图镇压反抗势力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去只会导致联邦独裁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们应该也很清楚这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是如此就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.88,0:13:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam居然再次出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道刹那也…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.00,0:13:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛丽娜·伊斯迈尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.39,0:13:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被拘捕了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==============================
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.11,0:13:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  为什么要将Celestial Being的资料告诉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这四年间  您到底是为了什么而做的这些准备
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们要是连这种程度的危机都无法度过的话  就没有意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.15,0:13:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐  比起改变世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您更像是在寻求战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  只有在战斗的尽头才会有世界的变革
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.38,0:13:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他们取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:14:00.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么  李本兹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:07.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真是不错的情报啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是Celestial Being的原特工
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:14.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要通知霍姆·片桐么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.61,0:14:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经找到了搭载Gundam的那艘飞船的坐标？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来自司令总部的情报  应该无误
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是片桐司令  做事就是滴水不漏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.75,0:14:34.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS全机出动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在起我舰将对Gundam的宇宙船发起奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD  第一第二小队  准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.72,0:14:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上尉  请给我出击的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是由我决定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就留下待机吧  哈莱维准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脚部的设定  没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.06,0:14:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:01.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD启动  各机赶快准备出发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.97,0:15:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AHEAD 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紧急暗号通信  是从托勒密上来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.83,0:15:29.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是王留美发来的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的位置被A-LAWS知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:32.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开Seravee出击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.73,0:15:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特你和伊恩尽快完成适配作业
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.34,0:15:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人部队接近  敌人部队接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗准备  战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会  要战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.31,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人部队接近  敌人部队接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.17,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗准备  战斗准备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.18,0:15:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二号弹射器  舱门已经打开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee  到达弹射轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电磁弹射器电压从230上升到520
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体位置固定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹射时机转交给Seravee
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.41,0:16:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解  Seravee  特瑞亚·埃德  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:19.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人编队
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.62,0:16:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是A-LAWS的MS吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:24.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那  我们的战力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.74,0:16:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有特瑞亚的机体  但有一台即将下线的新型机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有两机…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.75,0:16:33.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这组织还真够冷清的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾恩先生  诺瑞加小姐发来紧急暗号通信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.11,0:16:45.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺瑞加…  是皇小姐发来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:48.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是战术计划  离开始预定时间还有0032
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:50.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉强了
