Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  机体被…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.14,0:17:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从现在开始…啊！
