Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.18,0:17:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二小队去攻击运输舰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来对付Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  把OO开出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.24,0:18:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下  刹那  这边还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.94,0:18:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶操作就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备小型舰  同时进行OO的发射程序
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.75,0:18:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一弹射器舱门打开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.19,0:18:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是Celestial Being的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将OO运送至弹射轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:31.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.75,0:18:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO  搭载了O Gundam和EXIA的太阳炉的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:48.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Gundam
