Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还是用了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:13.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  粒子率停滞在73%
