Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干  干掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.39,0:19:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那道光是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那究竟是什么系统
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO Gundam  刹那·F·清荣  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型机？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:24.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用AHEAD击溃他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO  驱逐目标！
